{
  "text": "One of the aims of this study was deciphering the presence of benzoate derivatives. Particular heed was taken to the search for isoforms with the hydroxyl group replaced by a hydroxyl sulfate group in the benzoate side chain. These compounds would be designated as GC7-12. However, MS/MS analysis did not show their presence in the extracts analyzed, though the theoretical existence of more than 18 benzoate analogues was previously proposed [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "31192632"
